text: Eivor Berglund (born 22 September 1935) is a Swedish alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Sweden Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kramfors Municipality
